#####################
# Download Security #
#####################

You can see the MD5 and SHA1 hash (provided by sourceforge.net) after clicking the **I** button (View details).

If you login into sourceforge.net you can view this site over SSL.

If you care to GPG verify the download, get my GPG public key from multiple sources.

(1) ## Not forced through Tor, unless you are using Whonix, torsocks or similar.
gpg --keyserver x-hkp://pool.sks-keyservers.net --recv-keys 9B157153925C303A42253AFB9C131AD3713AAEEF

(2) https://raw.github.com/adrelanos/Whonix/master/adrelanos.asc

(3) more mirrors: https://sourceforge.net/p/whonix/wiki/TrustingWhonixSigningKey/

